Bootstrap: library
From: ubuntu:focal

%labels
    Author András Aszódi
    Version 1.3

%help
    Contains the various `multovl` executables. They are all statically linked
    so no extra software installation should be needed.
    The executables are the debug versions.

%post
    mkdir /multovl

%files
    # We _assume_ that the image will be built in the same directory as the executables
    ${PWD}/bin/file/multovl /multovl
    ${PWD}/bin/file/prob/*multovlprob /multovl

%environment
    PATH=/multovl:${PATH}

%runscript
    exec $@
